      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WRINKLED HENRY (1) is rarely out of the finish, recording 14 places from 27 starts. Finished in the money last time though when third (22.39) at this track. Got the money at his only try from this box. Makes plenty of appeal. OUT OF LUCK (6) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (18.70) at Wagga. Deserves a win and gets her chance. SKEDADDLE LULU (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Cool Rupee (31.99) in a Grade 5. Will give a great sight again. DEL MAR BOBBIE (7) defied the market to win last start and can measure up again.",
